"Claude Code SDK – Streaming JSON"

/desc
  This pipeline runs a Node script that connects to Anthropic via the Claude SDK
  and streams JSON events (NDJSON) as they arrive.
  
  Set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY before running. Optionally set PROMPT to customize input.
  
  Examples:
    MLLD_STREAM=full mlld examples/claude-code-streaming/claude-stream.mld
    PROMPT="Summarize this repo" \
    MLLD_STREAM=full mlld examples/claude-code-streaming/claude-stream.mld

/show "Starting Claude streaming example…"

/run { node examples/claude-code-streaming/stream.js }

/show "Finished."

